msgid "# triton.language.compile_hint"
msgstr "# triton.language.compile_hint"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:2
msgid "## 1.函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:4
msgid "`compile_hint` 是一个编译器提示（hint）机制，允许用户为张量附加元数据信息，这些信息会被传递到编译器后端，用于指导优化和代码生成。"
msgstr "`compile_hint` is a compiler hint mechanism that allows users to attach metadata information to tensors. This information is passed to the compiler backend to guide optimization and code generation."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.compile_hint(ptr, hint_name, hint_val=None, _builder=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:8
msgid "## 2.规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| `ptr` | `tensor` | 必需 | 需要附加提示的张量对象 |\n"
"| `hint_name` | `str` `constexpr` | 必需 | 提示的名称标识符（必须为字符串） |\n"
"| `hint_val` | `None` `bool` `int` `constexpr` `list` | `None` | 提示的值，支持多种类型 |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | `None` | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `ptr` | `tensor` | Required | The tensor object to which the hint is attached |\n"
"| `hint_name` | `str` `constexpr` | Required | Name identifier of the hint (must be a string) |\n"
"| `hint_val` | `None` `bool` `int` `constexpr` `list` | `None` | Value of the hint, supports multiple types |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | `None` | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:14
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:16
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/compile_hint.md:18
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
